# LMHY Engagement Agent Loop

When improving **letmehelpyourealtor.com** for engagement, run this checklist in order. Prefer measurable conversion paths over cosmetic-only edits.

## Engagement stack (do not duplicate)

| Tool | Location | Purpose |
|------|----------|---------|
| RealScout AI Search | `LMHYHero`, `layout.tsx` scripts | Property search |
| `LeadCaptureForm` | `QuickConnectSection`, `/contact` | FUB via `/api/leads/capture` |
| `AIChatWidget` | `EngagementLayer` in `layout.tsx` | AI Q&A → `/api/chat` |
| Calendly | `CalendlyBadge` (desktop), `/contact` widget | Scheduling |
| `MobileStickyCTA` | `EngagementLayer` | Mobile call / message / search |
| Widget tracker | `layout.tsx` | `WT-XQHVYQWW` |

Load engagement widgets **once** from `EngagementLayer` — never add a second chat or Calendly script on individual pages.

## Each optimization pass

1. **NAP + trust** — `lib/site-config.ts`: phone `(702) 500-1942`, email `DrDuffy@LetMeHelpYouRealtor.com`, GBP address; match visible copy + JSON-LD.
2. **CTA density** — Every money page needs: phone `tel:`, contact path, and search or lead form above the fold or within one scroll.
3. **Speed-to-lead** — Confirm `/api/leads/capture` tags include page source; FUB webhook `/api/webhooks/fub` healthy; SMS inbound `/api/webhooks/sms` when enabled.
4. **SEO / GSC** — 29 priority URLs in `lib/gsc-index-pages.ts`; canonical via `withPageCanonical` / `buildPageMetadata`; sitemap uses `www`.
5. **Core Web Vitals** — No duplicate third-party scripts; RealScout loaded once; images lazy-loaded.
6. **Content integrity** — June 2026 market stats from `lib/letmehelpyou-services.ts` / research JSON only; no fabricated review counts.

## Cursor loop usage

For recurring passes, use:

```
/loop 1d Audit LMHY engagement: CTAs, lead forms, GSC canonicals, FUB capture tags, SMS webhook, and mobile sticky bar on key pages. Fix highest-impact gap only.
```

Stack integrations (Notion, Twilio, AI advisor): see `lmhy-stack-loop.mdc`.

Or dynamic mode after deploy:

```
/loop Watch Vercel deploy then verify homepage lead form, chat widget, and /sitemap.xml on www.
```

## Out of scope without explicit approval

- Editing `/components/idx/*`
- Replacing `homes@heyberkshire.com` on security@ / info@ addresses
